passes.benefit_text:
Print from home
This coupon must be presented to Plimoth Patuxet Museums guest services staff upon arrival at the Museum for Memorial Hall Library patrons to purchase a Heritage Pass, Combination Pass, or Plimoth Patuxet Only pass for up to six individuals at the reduced rate of $16 per adult; $10 per child ages 5-17.&nbsp;
This coupon is for one time use only by the patron.

Pick up coupon at library.
Pass allows up to 6 people discounted admission ($9.00/adult and $6.00/child) to the Stone Zoo or the Franklin Park Zoo&nbsp;
Library coupon holders are no longer required to make a timed ticket reservation. Patrons may walk in with the library coupon and purchase tickets for the discounted rate.
